---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="ESP32 Drone Kit for STEM Education | Open Source Programmable Drone"
    description="Open source ESP32 drone kit for STEM education. Programmable drone with Wi-Fi control, complete tutorials from assembly to AI. Ideal for schools, makers, and drone education programs."
    lang="en"
>
    <header style="background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem 2rem;">
        <nav style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <a href="/" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-dark);">ESP32 Drone</a>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem;">
                <a href="/" style="font-weight: 600;">Home</a>
                <a href="/tutorials">Tutorials</a>
                <a href="/hardware">Hardware</a>
                <a href="/downloads">Downloads</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="/zh/">中文</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <main style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem;">
        <!-- Hero -->
        <section style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 2.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-dark);">
                ESP32 Open Source Drone<br>STEM Education Platform
            </h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-medium); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
                An open-source drone solution based on Espressif ESP32-S2/S3. 
                Supports Wi-Fi phone control with a complete STEM curriculum from assembly to AI.
            </p>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
                <a href="/tutorials" style="background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius); font-weight: 600;">Start Learning</a>
                <a href="/hardware" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius); color: var(--text-dark);">Explore Hardware</a>
                <a href="/downloads" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius); color: var(--text-dark);">Downloads</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Features -->
        <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📚</div>
                    <h3>3-Level Curriculum</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.9rem;">Beginner (Ready to Fly), Intermediate (Code & Tune), Advanced (AI & Algorithms)</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">💻</div>
                    <h3>ESP-IDF + Arduino</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.9rem;">Based on Crazyflie open-source firmware, ESP-IDF v5.0 framework</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📶</div>
                    <h3>Wi-Fi Control</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.9rem;">Built-in Wi-Fi hotspot, control via iOS/Android app</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🔧</div>
                    <h3>Open Hardware</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.9rem;">Complete schematics, PCB design, and 3D printable frame files</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Course Levels -->
        <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Graduated Learning Path</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-medium); margin-bottom: 2rem;">From "Learning by Playing" to "Creating by Learning", progressively unlock drone skills</p>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
                <!-- Beginner -->
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 1.5rem;">
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Beginner: Flight Explorer</h3>
                        <p style="opacity: 0.9;">Ready to fly, experience the joy</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Level</span>
                            <strong>Beginner</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Coding</span>
                            <strong>No coding</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Duration</span>
                            <strong>1-2 weeks</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Projects</span>
                            <strong>6 fun projects</strong>
                        </div>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            Assembly → LED/Sound → Path Plan → FPV → Tracking → Formation
                        </p>
                        <a href="/tutorials" style="background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: var(--radius); display: block; text-align: center;">Start Learning</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Intermediate -->
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 1.5rem;">
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Intermediate: Flight Engineer</h3>
                        <p style="opacity: 0.9;">Modify code, understand flight control</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Level</span>
                            <strong>Intermediate</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Coding</span>
                            <strong>Basic C</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Duration</span>
                            <strong>1-2 months</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Projects</span>
                            <strong>6 advanced projects</strong>
                        </div>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            Code Mod → PID Tune → Sensors → Avoidance → Telemetry → Plotting
                        </p>
                        <a href="/tutorials/intermediate" style="background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: var(--radius); display: block; text-align: center;">Start Learning</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Advanced -->
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 1.5rem;">
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Advanced: Flight Scientist</h3>
                        <p style="opacity: 0.9;">Algorithm design, system integration</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Level</span>
                            <strong>Advanced</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Coding</span>
                            <strong>C + Python</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Duration</span>
                            <strong>2-3 months</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-light);">Projects</span>
                            <strong>7 challenge projects</strong>
                        </div>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            Path Planning → VIO → Tracking → AI → MESH → Formation → Autonomy
                        </p>
                        <a href="/tutorials/advanced" style="background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: var(--radius); display: block; text-align: center;">Start Learning</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
